+|-----------|-------|
+| CVE ID | CVE-2021-26539 |
+| Status | **NOT APPLICABLE** |
+| Target Version | sanitize-html v1.4.2 |
+| Vulnerable Feature | `allowedIframeHostnames` |
+| Feature Present in v1.4.2 | **NO** |
